{"tid":1598354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一張圖話你知點解要「一」區大遊行（唔一定要港島）","createTime":"2019-09-27T11:45:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T17:09:05.000Z","uid":190579,"like":110,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"e9c62b70a7b2793eed8e2a2ea9d968766d9ee2bc","tid":1598354,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:45:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>TLDR<br />\n早D起身 <br />\n先集中一區和理非<br />\n否則唔使旨意再有外媒關注香港<br />\n後散去各區勇武</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/fq5SFTf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffq5SFTf.png&h=722eddcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMark Simon係黎智英助手, 亦係美國共和黨的長期黨員.<br />\n<br />\n而家, Mark Simon話:<br />\n- 近兩日, 已有美國兩大媒體取消派員來香港採訪示威.<br />\n- 如香港長期只有少數人參與的抗爭行動, 是吸引不到美國媒體的注視.<br />\n- 而家, <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港急需一場大型遊行, 參與人數起碼要有接近一百萬</strong></span>. &amp;nbsp;這場大型遊行, 可令廣大美國媒體重新注意香港抗爭.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"http://twitter.com/HKMarkSimon/status/1176733306924064768\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKMarkSimon%2Fstatus%2F1176733306924064768&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHd6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=70241111\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKMarkSimon%2Fstatus%2F1176733306924064768&h=68202f3e\" target=\"_blank\">http://twitter.com/HKMarkSimon/status/1176733306924064768</a><br />\n共和黨成員: 美國兩大媒體已取消採訪「香港示威」. &nbsp;香港急需一場大型遊行.<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1593703\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1593703</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">行街睇戲食飯</span></strong></span>關你撚事咩死警犬，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>唔需要佢哋批准</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n和理非既唔使驚，拉我咪踢保囉，只係48個鐘<br />\n我只係嚟行街睇戲食飯，根本告唔入<br />\n連被捕決心都冇<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">（已經唔係講坐監，只係被捕）</span>，就唔好叫自己和理非啦，都唔好叫咩光復香港時代革命啦，只係一個懦夫<br />\n戴耀廷，陳虹秀呢d先叫和理非<br />\n<br />\n勇武做乜都得，就係唔准幫和理殿後，一早咪講好左<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和理為矛勇武為盾</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n早D起身，起碼要集中人數行一次先，務求入黑前散水<br />\n之後番自己區做嘢"},{"pid":"b64eb4ce04d394455ea0a05a285dfa61bc93bcfa","tid":1598354,"uid":190579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:46:01.000Z","msg":"一區行街"},{"pid":"3ffa68305976c248e66a935ada1aae549be8a23f","tid":1598354,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:46:12.000Z","msg":"一區行街"},{"pid":"beca0ae4386ad2f69f93d8c698a14be48f7105a5","tid":1598354,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:46:22.000Z","msg":"一區行街"},{"pid":"d402dc620e9a98742badaa22337a2522921036e1","tid":1598354,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:46:59.000Z","msg":"一區行街"},{"pid":"2bf07d5d8f96caef0345c5c2c556459b91cd983c","tid":1598354,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:51:05.000Z","msg":"一張圖話你知點解要「一」區大遊行（唔一定要港島）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1598354\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1598354</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2bbb9e537e991f9f15ad3e6af630105303b4499e","tid":1598354,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:54:11.000Z","msg":"入嚟討論"},{"pid":"aec37570d2e506955d95b4584e64e58e13121883","tid":1598354,"uid":119568,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:05:09.000Z","msg":"一區過<br />\n<br />\n1.分散出？影相出嚟邊夠二百萬人威？<br />\n<br />\n2.各區人少，警真係唔撚驚你，反正勇武一定唔多，俾錢叫白衫做嘢都得<br />\n<br />\n3.記者去邊好？夠唔夠？外國記者又揀邊區去？<br />\n<br />\n4. 二百萬人，好難控制，開錯槍搞到要 血慶國家咩...."},{"pid":"11d0ace8b3ca71e6308665a84ed37c76020255a5","tid":1598354,"uid":71423,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:08:25.000Z","msg":"Exactly <br />\n當日係十一國殤<br />\n更加要用人數去話比全世界知<br />\n五區集會的確係做到撚狗效果 不過平時星期六日都做到同樣效果<br />\n但十一係一個重要日子 <br />\n重點係要<span style=\"color: red;\">對準政權</span>"},{"pid":"a8a4930f0aaff3b2c894e8ef7f1c8104e70bb3e8","tid":1598354,"uid":143321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:11:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ccaadfd4403feb9691c32c593c595aa9858cde7","tid":1598354,"uid":294,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:14:08.000Z","msg":"929 一區<br />\n101多區"},{"pid":"7d3b94f1ed6b0a95f250f897c8494c068bc53818","tid":1598354,"uid":278057,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:14:26.000Z","msg":"講得岩！"},{"pid":"2235a6f077c9a6c78242fb409682f94c29d6c6b3","tid":1598354,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:14:57.000Z","msg":"而家唔批呀大佬<br />\n<br />\n梗係行plan B啦"},{"pid":"4ad790a2071f1b566b6bbe9f52638423414e1276","tid":1598354,"uid":12824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:14:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9b7d210f2ccd582b98e4a3ec12f9384e5a68ddc","tid":1598354,"uid":51293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:15:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"137bba53868eab68bca3e9bb4c348331cb1e4831","tid":1598354,"uid":16137,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:15:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dee4b3ae2660da484597ab911584ede331907492","tid":1598354,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9ccaadfd4403feb9691c32c593c595aa9858cde7","tid":1598354,"uid":294,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:14:08.000Z","msg":"929 一區<br />\n101多區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:15:32.000Z","msg":"support"},{"pid":"359548b4bf00c907b00a0c1875